{"tid":2315400,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用家投訴 iPhone 12 系列信號差  Apple：轉台以解決問題","createTime":"2020-12-07T07:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T13:29:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"016c048a6de1998fc24abde7dd22cda41b181085","tid":2315400,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Screen_Shot_2020_10_14_at_3.23.07_PM.0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FScreen_Shot_2020_10_14_at_3.23.07_PM.0.jpeg&h=b75918d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple 最新的 iPhone 12 系列，除採用 A14 晶片外，其力推的賣點應是支援 5G 網絡，不過，有不少 iPhone 12 用家表示其新電話的信號相當差，不但無法使用 5G 網絡，連打電話也成問題。<br />\n<br />\n近日 Reddit 討論區不乏投訴 iPhone 12 信號差的討論串，用戶們表示，其 iPhone 12 經常在 5G 、4G 兩者頻密自動切換，甚至出現過斷網、無信號的情況，更嚴重者連 Wi-Fi 也無法連接，要重新啟動電話才可以正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n而除了上網問題，有用戶表示打電話也會間歇性出現障礙，有時候需要步出房外才可收到信號，但使用同樣電訊商 Sim 卡的 Android 電話就沒有相關問題。<br />\n<br />\n有用戶曾向電訊商投訴求助，而電訊商 職員只回應指是 iPhone 問題，但 Apple 售後服務就轉而指是電訊商問題，甚至喚有相關問題的用戶更換電訊商以處理相關情況，似乎各 iPhone 12 用家距離真正解決問題可謂遙遙無期。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：9to5Mac<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/06/iphone-12-signal/fun-tech/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F06%2Fiphone-12-signal%2Ffun-tech%2F%3F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYToICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=9fd46389\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/06/iphone-12-signal/fun-tech/?</a>"},{"pid":"b3b999c50548264a80e01c1a442275ce19b7e3f8","tid":2315400,"uid":28114,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"責任全在買方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aead46d68a8bea0125838a3c4a345f51f6afb75","tid":2315400,"uid":180401,"like":9,"dislike":1,"scor